Transmutation
Level: Animal 7, Druid 8
Casting Time: 1 action
Range: Close (25 ft + 5ft/lvl)
Targets: One willing creature
Duration: 1 hour/level
Saving Throw: None (see text)
Spell Resistance: Yes (harmless)

As polymorph other, except you polymorph one willing creature into an animal of your choice, the spell has no effect on unwilling creatures. Recipients remain in the animal form until the spell expires.